Package xmlParser

Class HistoryXMLManipulation

java.lang.Object
xmlParser.ContainerXMLManipulation
xmlParser.HistoryXMLManipulation
All Implemented Interfaces:
GeneralPersistency<Container>, IdentifiablePersistency<Container>
public class HistoryXMLManipulation
extends ContainerXMLManipulation
This class implements the database for the historical record of containers. It implements the singleton pattern, and is supposed to be used through the GeneralPersistency interface. It is one of the four entry points to the xmlParser package.
Author:
simon
